                                <p>Use our tracking system with your tracking ID. You'll receive updates via email and SMS. You can also call our 24/7 support team for detailed shipment information and status.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <div class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">
